# Java Standards
- Follow standard Java conventions.
- Avoid god classes.
- Keep responsibilities clear.

## Structure
- Max ~200 lines per class.
- Extract services/helpers when exceeded.

## Architecture
- controller → service → repository
- No business logic in controllers.

## Safety
- Do not change behavior without confirmation.
- Explain risks before modifying.
